// gtk_cell_area_cell_set() or gtk_cell_area_cell_set_valist(). To obtain the
// value of a cell property, use gtk_cell_area_cell_get_property(),
// gtk_cell_area_cell_get() or gtk_cell_area_cell_get_valist().
