//    @content_area as an internal child with the name â€œcontent_areaâ€.
//
//    GtkDialog supports a custom <action-widgets> element, which can contain
//    multiple <action-widget> elements. The â€œresponseâ€ attribute specifies a
//    numeric response, and the content of the element is the id of widget
//    (which should be a child of the dialogs @action_area). To mark a response
//    as default, set the â€œdefaultâ€œ attribute of the <action-widget> element
//    to true.
//
